OL,3,CCutting taxes will lead to worse
OL,4,Cpublic services, IFS warns ahead of
OL,5,Cbudget
OL,7,FUnsportingly, it refuses to even
OL,8,Fhazard a guess. Instead, it wants to
OL,9,Ftalk about trade-offs.
OL,11,FIf the chancellor does insist on
OL,12,Fcutting taxes on March 6 then the IFS
OL,13,Fsays he should also be honest about
OL,14,Fwhat the consequences will be.
OL,16,FNot least for public services, which
OL,17,Fthe IFS argues are showing clear signs
OL,18,Fof creaking.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G2/17
