OL,3,CCutting taxes will lead to worse
OL,4,Cpublic services, IFS warns ahead of
OL,5,Cbudget
OL,7,F"We have huge backlogs in the Justice
OL,8,Fsystem and local authorities are going
OL,9,Fbust, left, right and centre," says
OL,10,FPaul Johnson, Director of the IFS.
OL,12,F"We have huge waiting lists in the
OL,13,Fhealth service; universities who are
OL,14,Fincreasingly, I think, genuinely
OL,15,Fstarting to struggle with more than
OL,16,Ften years of frozen income; a social
OL,17,Fcare system which is struggling and
OL,18,Fquite dependent on immigration, which
OL,19,Fnone of the parties seem terribly keen
OL,20,Fon; and a prison system that is full".
