OL,3,CCutting taxes will lead to worse
OL,4,Cpublic services, IFS warns ahead of
OL,5,Cbudget
OL,7,FThe chancellor seems determined to cut
OL,8,Feither National Insurance or Income
OL,9,FTax next week.
OL,11,FAnd he appears to be preparing to
OL,12,Fcreate the room he needs to do this
OL,13,Fagainst his fiscal target (to get
OL,14,Fnational debt falling as a share of
OL,15,Fnational income in five years time) by
OL,16,Fmaking cuts to departmental spending
OL,17,Fon public services after the election.
OL,19,FThe IFS implies that such a plan is
OL,20,Fboth unwise and unworkable.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G4/17
