OL,7,FAs it stands, real-terms (adjusted for
OL,8,Finflation) spending on public services
OL,9,Fis set to rise by 0.9% a year on
OL,10,Faverage from next April onwards.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G5/17
