OL,3,CCutting taxes will lead to worse
OL,4,Cpublic services, IFS warns ahead of
OL,5,Cbudget
OL,7,FBut the IFS points out that if you
OL,8,Ffactor in the new, higher population
OL,9,Fprojections that the Office for
OL,10,FNational Statistics has published and
OL,11,Fassume that budgets for the NHS,
OL,12,Fchildcare, defence, schools and
OL,13,Foverseas aid will continue to be
OL,14,Feither protected or enhanced in ways
OL,15,Fwhich have already been announced,
OL,16,Fthen the reality is other areas of
OL,17,Fgovernment spending face an even
OL,18,Ftighter squeeze on resources.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G6/17
