OL,3,CCutting taxes will lead to worse
OL,4,Cpublic services, IFS warns ahead of
OL,5,Cbudget
OL,7,FYou can understand the government's
OL,8,Fdesire to cut taxes.
OL,10,FAllowing people to retain more of
OL,11,Ftheir earnings in the run-up to a
OL,12,Fgeneral election is likely to be
OL,13,Fpopular.
OL,15,FAnd the tax "burden" in the UK -
OL,16,Fmeasured as a share of national income
OL,17,F- has risen sharply during this
OL,18,Fparliament and is on course to rise to
OL,19,Freach its highest level since 1948.
OL,26,@wD@MOUwD@TO]
