OL,4,Cpublic services, IFS warns ahead of
OL,5,Cbudget
OL,7,FThe government is currently raising
OL,8,F#66 billion a year more in tax than it
OL,9,Fwas in 2018/19 but the IFS says it's
OL,10,Fdifficult to see how the overall
OL,11,Fburden can easily be reduced.
OL,13,F'Higher taxes look like they are going
OL,14,Fto be a permanent rather than
OL,15,Ftemporary feature'
OL,17,F"(Higher taxes) looks to us like a
OL,18,Fpermanent rather than a temporary
OL,19,Ffeature," says Carl Emmerson, Deputy
OL,20,FDirector of The IFS.
OL,26,@yD@BpmyD@Opn{D@IO]
