OL,3,CCutting taxes will lead to worse
OL,4,Cpublic services, IFS warns ahead of
OL,5,Cbudget
OL,7,F"The government is spending more on
OL,8,Fservicing the national debt, the
OL,9,Fgovernment is busily expanding the
OL,10,Fprogramme of childcare, the NHS is
OL,11,Frequiring more and more resources each
OL,12,Fyear, as is social care...it seems
OL,13,Fhard to see where significant spending
OL,14,Fcuts would come from (on a scale) that
OL,15,Fwould be required to finance a
OL,16,Fsubstantial reduction in the tax
OL,17,Fburden".
