OL,3,CCutting taxes will lead to worse
OL,4,Cpublic services, IFS warns ahead of
OL,5,Cbudget
OL,7,FThe tax rises of the last few years
OL,8,Fhave helped to fund the extraordinary
OL,9,Famount of financial support (#500
OL,10,Fbillion) that the government has made
OL,11,Favailable for households and
OL,12,Fbusinesses.
OL,14,FPrivately, the chancellor accepts that
OL,15,Fnot all of these can be rolled back.
OL,17,FPublicly, he is committed to pursuing
OL,18,Fwhat he calls "smart" tax cuts - those
OL,19,Fwhich boost the supply side of the
OL,20,Feconomy and increase growth.
OL,26,@zD@OOUzD@UO]
