OL,3,CCutting taxes will lead to worse
OL,4,Cpublic services, IFS warns ahead of
OL,5,Cbudget
OL,7,FReducing either National Insurance or
OL,8,FIncome Tax appears to be his
OL,9,Fpreference.
OL,11,FThe IFS says that while both taxes
OL,12,Fwould stimulate growth, neither would
OL,13,Fbe self-financing.
OL,15,F"A genuine tax cut is going to require
OL,16,Fsome spending cuts to help pay for
OL,17,Fit," says Emmerson.
OL,26,@wD@AOUyD@DO]
