OL,3,CCutting taxes will lead to worse
OL,4,Cpublic services, IFS warns ahead of
OL,5,Cbudget
OL,7,FHe would also be leaving government
OL,8,Fdebt at a level which is high and
OL,9,Frising in the short-term and barely
OL,10,Ffalling five years, which carries risk.
OL,12,FThe expected path of interest rates in
OL,13,Fthe UK is lower than it was at the
OL,14,FAutumn Statement but the future is
OL,15,Fimpossible to predict and the
OL,16,Fgovernment still looks set to be
OL,17,Fspending #55 billion a year more
OL,18,Fservicing its debts than the OBR
OL,19,Fforecast just three years ago - which
OL,20,Fis roughly the equivalent of the
OL,21,Fannual defence budget.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G14/17
