OL,3,CCutting taxes will lead to worse
OL,4,Cpublic services, IFS warns ahead of
OL,5,Cbudget
OL,7,FIn his Autumn Statement, the
OL,8,Fchancellor used the benefits of high
OL,9,Finflation (higher tax revenues) to cut
OL,10,Ftaxes while ignoring the costs (more
OL,11,Fpressure on the budgets of departments
OL,12,Fwhich deliver public services).
OL,14,FThe IFS says there's a danger that, in
OL,15,Fthis Budget, Jeremy Hunt's next
OL,16,F"trick" will be to "bank the higher
OL,17,Frevenue which come from a larger
OL,18,Fpopulation while ignoring the
OL,19,Fadditional pressures that a larger
OL,20,Fpopulation puts on the NHS, local
OL,21,Fgovernment and other services".
