OL,7,FNext week, we may end up in the odd
OL,8,F(and the IFS would argue
OL,9,Funsatisfactory) situation where the
OL,10,Fgovernment announces a tax cut or cuts
OL,11,Fwhich it knows may need to be reversed
OL,12,Fif it wins the next election.
OL,14,FAnd where Labour votes to support
OL,15,Fthose tax cuts, with the clear
OL,16,Funderstanding it may have to do the
OL,17,Fsame.
